      <ownedComment xmi:id="e8872402-5462-45cc-a917-5bcb80e232ee" body="A boundary is a class that lies on the periphery of a system, but within it. It interacts with actors outside the system as well as with entity, control, and other boundary classes within the system." annotatedElement="3a0f8317-5e15-4dd0-a3a8-75a222be3f54">
